thumb.title: Cefali & Cefali Personal Injury Lawyers
thumb.description: Cefali & Cefali are personal injury attorneys located in Orange County, California, specifically in the city of San Juan Capistrano. The firm handles every kind of personal injury case including car accidents, trucking accidents, bicycle accidents, motorcycle accidents, boating accidents, pedestrian accidents, rideshare accidents, slip and fall cases, whiplash injuries, dog bite injuries, accidents involving brain injuries, assault and battery injuries, and accidents involving DUI or DWI. The law firm is pleased to help the people of Orange County, CA and the cities within Orange County such as Mission Viejo, Dana Point, Newport Beach, Laguna Beach, Lake Forest, San Clemente, Laguna Niguel, Aliso Viejo, Moreno Valley, and Irvine.Cefali & Cefali Personal Injury Lawyers27136 Paseo Espada, Suite 1123, San Juan Capistrano, CA 92675, United States949-325-7790https://callcefali.com/
